Sentence: an airport in key west , florida , today became the setting of what appeared to be a desperate attempt to enter the u . s. by a cuban national. the man was arrested there after authorities say he hijacked a cuban plane using what was reported to be grenades , ordering the pilots to fly to florida. the hijacker got off the plane wearing a jacket that said , america across the back. and a small child clinging to his leg .
